                        <p class="section-kicker mb-2">Why guests return</p>
                        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4">A bakery experience guests trust.</h2>
                        <div class="highlight-preview" style="background:#fffdf9; border:1px solid rgba(182,106,60,0.14); border-radius:28px; padding:1.8rem 1.6rem; box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(91,52,33,0.06);" aria-live="polite">
                            <span class="highlight-preview-label">Featured feedback</span>
                            <p class="highlight-preview-text mb-0" data-highlight-preview>
                                The menu is easy to browse and the cakes are always beautifully presented.
